Titolo: Lego Island

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Lego Island is a Lego-themed action-adventure game developed and published by Mindscape. It was released for Microsoft Windows on September 26, 1997, as the first Lego video game outside Japan. It received positive reviews and inspired several preservationists and other fans, and was followed by two sequels: Lego Island 2: The Brickster's Revenge (2001) and Island Xtreme Stunts (2002).